data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the desirable neighborhood of Halls Creek North! This stunning 5-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home boasts an abundance of space, offering the perfect haven to enjoy life to the fullest. PLUS, $1,500 USE AS YOU CHOOSE ALLOWANCE!!As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and welcoming ambiance. The main level features a versatileflex space with elegant French doors, ideal for a home office or any extra living space you desire. The formal dining room sets the stage for memorable gatherings and special occasions.The heart of the home is the oversized family room, complete with a cozy gas fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for relaxation and quality time with loved ones. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a walk-in pantry, granite countertops, and ample space for culinary creativity. The adjacent breakfast nook provides a lovely spot to enjoy casual meals and morning coffee.The main level also boasts a convenient laundry/mud room and a half bath. Upstairs, all five generously sized bedrooms await, ensuring everyone has their own comfortable retreat. The bedroom over the garage is a versatile space, perfect for entertaining guests or transforming into a game or media room for endless fun and enjoyment.The master bedroom is a true sanctuary, featuring a tray ceiling and his and her closets, providing ample storage for your wardrobe. The en-suite bathroom offers a luxurious soaking tub, inviting you to unwind and relax after a long day.Outdoor living is a delight with the screened porch, offering a bug-free oasis for relaxation and socializing. The stone patio with a firepit sets the stage for cozy gatherings under the stars, making it the perfect spot for roasting marshmallows and sharing stories with friends and family. The large backyard is enclosed with a privacy fence, ensuring your own private oasis for outdoor activities and play.Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
